name: Selective Identity: Transgressions
description:
"Selective Identity: Transgressions," 2022, JPEG (from series)
This photo collage was created in 2018 while applying to different MFA programs in the US.  I began to notice the questions that they asked, and decided to put those questions on my body as brand.  These are real screen shots of application questions some of the top MFA programs in the US were asking at this time.
